[32m│[0m `FLAG{b5b4759907706b68a92b4ae6015033897f29c0ea134d8a59a412d36aab2456e0}`     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The application has a **vulnerable authentication mechanism** that accepts   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m user_id as a client-side parameter, allowing an attacker to enumerate and    [32m│[0m
