[32m│[0m [+] VALID: user_id=10032 - Successful authentication (302 redirect to        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m /dashboard)                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Dashboard Content for user_id=10001:                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <h5 class="card-title">Welcome, Flag                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m FLAG{b5b4759907706b68a92b4ae6015033897f29c0ea134d8a59a412d36aab2456e0}</h5>  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Dashboard Content for user_id=10032:                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <h5 class="card-title">Welcome, John Doe</h5>                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Authentication Flow:                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Valid auth**: `POST /password/test` → HTTP 302 to `/dashboard` + session [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m cookie set                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Invalid auth**: `POST /password/test` → HTTP 302 to `/` (no session      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m cookie)                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
